name: Electricity Consumption report All Schools
query:
select
    site as "TCIL Code",
    udise_code as "UDISE Code",
    site_name as "School name",
    district as "District",
    block as "Block",
    date as "Date of Posting Bill",
    main_meter_previous_reading as "Main Meter Previous month reading",
    main_meter_current_reading as "Main Meter Current month reading",
    previous_meter_reading as "Sub Meter Previous month reading",
    meter_reading as "Sub Meter Current month reading",
    price_per_unit as "Price per unit",
    date as "Bill Posting Date",
    payment_date as "Date of Bill Payment",
    transaction_id as "Transaction ID"
from `tabElectricity Consumption Record`;
